name: Wild Horse Mustang
description:
Horses are lovable animals and have long sought to tame them alongside humans.  The best friend of soldiers in wars, the most diligent in agriculture and the best means of travel for travelers.

 He is called noble, perhaps because of the love he expresses to his master, or perhaps because of his secret love for human beings.  Throughout history, horses have had a profound effect on human social evolution, from the first domesticated horses to the great wars that led to the existence of horses, such as the victories of the Mongols and the skill of using horses in battle.  .

 There are several breeds of this type of horse in different parts of the world, each of which has acquired its own special and extraordinary characteristics during evolution.
